The activelock XML element per the WebDAV specification [RFC 4918] 

    Name:       activelock
    Namespace:  DAV:
    Purpose:    Describes a lock on a resource.
    <!ELEMENT activelock (lockscope, locktype, depth, owner?, timeout?, locktoken?) <
